# {{ ansible_managed }}
# Overrides the nginx package's logrotate config: its postrotate signals the
# HOST nginx pid, which no longer exists - the k3s nginx would keep writing
# to the rotated file forever. copytruncate needs no signal at all.
/var/log/nginx/*.log {
        daily
        missingok
        rotate 14
        compress
        delaycompress
        notifempty
        copytruncate
}
